title: A Bunch of Jon Peniel Spiritual Books (atlantis.to)
description:
Jon Peniel is an amazing spiritual author, his main book is "The Children of The Law of One and the Lost Teachings of Atlantis", it is life changing, read it and you'll be a kinder, happier, more spiritual person guaranteed. The rest of his books are much shorter and about certain topics but are still spiritually insightful. I bought all of these books except for Lost Teachings of Atlantis.

Included:
- The Children of The Law of One and the Lost Teachings of Atlantis
- Sex and the Spiritual Guy (or Woman)
- Primal Power Tantra
- The New Male Orgasm (not actually by him but sold on his wbesite)
- The Last Days of Atlantis (fiction)
- Aliens and UFOs Parts 1 - 3

These are also all available on my Scribd profile http://www.scribd.com/people/documents/8111491/folder/99407
